01:24:08,628 --> 01:24:11,945
-Doctore Hahn, felicitari.

1068
01:24:14,189 --> 01:24:19,115
-Vroiam 
sa fii prima care afla.

1069
01:24:19,778 --> 01:24:22,959
-Ma bucur pentru tine,

1070
01:24:23,960 --> 01:24:25,960
foarte mult.

